148
00:12:34.300 --> 00:12:40.779
John Hasse: And I went to, to crash business training at the Wharton School at the University of Pennsylvania.

149
00:12:41.000 --> 00:12:44.089
John Hasse: and was hired by Procter & Gamble in Marketing Management.

150
00:12:44.670 --> 00:12:50.499
John Hasse: And that didn't work out after 13 months. They actually had me leave the company.

151
00:12:51.130 --> 00:12:56.290
