00:14:06.240 --> 00:14:11.470
John Hasse: Well, like… Let's see, graduated Carleton in 1971.

165
00:14:11.740 --> 00:14:14.819
John Hasse: Worked in the Twin Cities in a presidential campaign.

166
00:14:15.290 --> 00:14:20.400
John Hasse: for 2 years, and after the campaign ended, I had a series of odd jobs.

167
00:14:20.510 --> 00:14:22.670
John Hasse: Went on the road with a rock.

168
00:14:22.800 --> 00:14:24.990
John Hasse: slash show band.

169
00:14:25.270 --> 00:14:27.660
John Hasse: I worked in a paint factory for a week.

170
00:14:27.960 --> 00:14:34.250
John Hasse: Of her big fats of… of, poisonous fumes, ugh.

171
00:14:34.490 --> 00:14:37.510
John Hasse: Then I was, attempt.

