00:22:20.540 --> 00:22:22.030
John Hasse: Parents had been teachers, and…

265
00:22:22.070 --> 00:22:23.070
Julie Stout: Right.

266
00:22:23.320 --> 00:22:29.490
John Hasse: One of my… two of my sisters were teachers, and… My family revered education.

267
00:22:30.630 --> 00:22:34.069
John Hasse: I got called out for one interview, it was at UCLA.

268
00:22:35.160 --> 00:22:46.949
John Hasse: They wanted somebody not to do research, they wanted somebody to sort of babysit babysit a,

269
00:22:47.100 --> 00:22:52.879
John Hasse: Class of 500 undergraduates, including… a lot of jocks, or athletes.

